data.description: Welcome to the remarkably cared for 2 bedrooms ranch with full basement just minutes from Ashtabula Harbor. This home boasts a gorgeous setting for all the backyard BBQ's and yard games in the fully fenced in yard with an oversized paver patio. There is over 1,000 square feet on the main floor and a full basement for all of your storage or extra 'hangout-space' needs. The oversized eat-in kitchen features newer cabinets and corian countertops with all kitchen appliances staying. This is a wonderful place to call home!
